headline: RayNeo solidifies its global AR market leadership in Q3 with a 24% share
summary: RayNeo has solidified its leadership in the consumer augmented reality (AR) sector, achieving top positions in both market share and seasonal sales. According to the latest Q3 2025 Global AR Smart Glasses Brand Shipment Share Report from Counterpoint Research, RayNeo ranked No. 1 worldwide for the second consecutive quarter, capturing a 24.5% market share.
